It’s been an incredible 2 year journey making THE RESCUE. Excited to finally share the trailer. (Check the link in my bio for more info.) THE RESCUE chronicles the against-all-odds story that held the world breathless in 2018 – the daring rescue of twelve soccer players and their coach from deep inside a flooded cave in Northern Thailand.

Big shout out to our amazing crew and in particular the best co-director one could ask for @chaivasarhelyi for the tireless efforts bringing this film and story to life.

I hope you enjoy the trailer. See #TheRescueFilm in theaters this October. therescue.film @natgeodocs | @freesolofilm

In my early twenties I was lucky enough to get on a @NOLSedu course. It had a big impact on my life direction at the time and inspired me in a way I had not found elsewhere. I eventually taught at NOLS for several years. I found teaching at NOLS to be deeply satisfying and I can’t say enough about the growth a student (young or old) can gain on one of their courses. I got to see it first hand. Now I am fortunate enough to sit on the board because I truly believe NOLS is an organization that helps people on their path to finding their greatest potential. #thetrailtosuccess

Link in bio to learn more.

And of course, Steph is still an awesome rope gun and all around badass! Check it: http://bit.ly/OSMO_JC or hit the link in my bio. #sponsored.

It’s been an incredible 2 year journey making THE RESCUE. Excited to finally share the trailer. (Check the link in my bio for more info.) THE RESCUE chronicles the against-all-odds story that held the world breathless in 2018 – the daring rescue of twelve soccer players and their coach from deep inside a flooded cave in Northern Thailand.

Big shout out to our amazing crew and in particular the best co-director one could ask for @chaivasarhelyi for the tireless efforts bringing this film and story to life.

I hope you enjoy the trailer. See #TheRescueFilm in theaters this October. therescue.film @natgeodocs | @freesolofilm
